OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778677871
OL,3,CITV News tracks 64 MPs prepared to
OL,4,Coust PM
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FAt least 64 MPs are prepared to oust
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer, as he faces ongoing
OL,11,Fquestions around his leadership in the
OL,12,Fwake of last week's devastating
OL,13,Felection results for the Labour Party.
OL,15,FITV News has spoken to and tracked
OL,16,Fonline 56 MPs who think the prime
OL,17,Fminister should immediately set out a
OL,18,Ftimeline for his departure - and a
OL,19,Ffurther eight who believe he should
OL,20,Fleave if things do not improve.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
