OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778677871
OL,3,CITV News tracks 64 MPs prepared to
OL,4,Coust PM
OL,6,FIn a message sent to all members of
OL,7,Fthe parliamentary Labour Party, ITV
OL,8,FNews asked whether, in the wake of a
OL,9,Fspeech delivered by the PM on Monday
OL,10,Fmorning, they still had confidence
OL,11,FStarmer was the right person to lead
OL,12,Ftheir party.
OL,14,FIn responses made publicly online, and
OL,15,Fgiven directly to ITV News, nearly 15%
OL,16,Fof Labour MPs said they did not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
