OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778677871
OL,3,CITV News tracks 64 MPs prepared to
OL,4,Coust PM
OL,6,FIn a speech on Monday, the prime
OL,7,Fminister told the British public
OL,8,F"incremental change won't cut it", as
OL,9,Fhe pledged to go further on defence,
OL,10,Fenergy and in forging closer ties with
OL,11,FEurope.
OL,13,FHis words came against a backdrop of a
OL,14,Fleadership challenge ultimatum from
OL,15,Fbackbench MP Catherine West, who
OL,16,Fdescribed the speech as "too little
OL,17,Ftoo late".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
