PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778677871
OL,3,CITV News tracks 64 MPs prepared to
OL,4,Coust PM
OL,6,FWest herself initially promised to
OL,7,Flaunch her own leadership bid in an
OL,8,Fattempt to force a cabinet member to
OL,9,Fstand down.
OL,11,FShe has since appeared to ride back on
OL,12,Fthese threats, instead messaging
OL,13,FLabour colleagues to ask for their
OL,14,Fsupport in urging the PM to set out a
OL,15,Ftimeframe for his departure.
OL,17,FAt the time of writing, ITV News has
OL,18,Fspoken to and tracked at least 64 MPs
OL,19,Fwho agree with West's proposal for the
OL,20,FPM to go, or say that if things don't
OL,21,Fchange soon, he should leave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
