OL,3,CITV News tracks 64 MPs prepared to
OL,4,Coust PM
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLabour MPs need 81 publicly recorded
OL,12,Fnames to trigger a leadership
OL,13,Fchallenge, a contest Starmer told
OL,14,Fjournalists on Monday he would fight
OL,15,Fin were it to take place.
OL,17,FSome MPs argue the timing of West's
OL,18,Fthreats to Labour leadership risks a
OL,19,F"cabinet stitch-up", and serves to
OL,20,Fbenefit certain potential leadership
OL,21,Fcandidates more than others.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
