OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778677871
OL,3,CITV News tracks 64 MPs prepared to
OL,4,Coust PM
OL,6,FThe PM's speech was followed by a
OL,7,Fspeech from one potential leadership
OL,8,Fcandidate, Angela Rayner, who was
OL,9,Fspeaking at a union conference in
OL,10,FBournemouth.
OL,12,FRayner said more change was needed,
OL,13,Fwith a return to core Labour values,
OL,14,Fand argued the decision to block the
OL,15,FManchester Mayor, Andy Burnham, from
OL,16,Freturning to parliament as an MP was a
OL,17,Fmistake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
